## Contacts [/api/UponorInternet/Contact{?language,type}]

+ Parameters
    + language: `de-de` (string, required) - Language code in which should the contacts be displayed
    + type (enum[string], optional) - Contact type filter
        + Members
            + `academy`
            + `uponorandmore`
            + `customerservice`
            + `technicalhotline`

### Get some [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
        
        {
            Name: "Contact Service",
            IsoCode: "de-DE",
            Values: [
                {
                    ContactType: "academy",
                    ContactName: "Academy",
                    ContactPhone: "+ 49 800 7780050 ",
                    ContactFax: "",
                    ContactMobile: "",
                    ContactMailLink: {
                        LinkDescription: "academy@uponor.com",
                        Mailto: "academy@uponor.com",
