# Data Structures

## News item (object)
+ id (string) - Item unique id
+ title (string) - Item title
+ description (string) - item perex (short description)
+ mediaType (string) - mediaFile type
+ mediaFile (string) - URL to media file
+ mediaFileThumb (string) - URL to media file type
+ url (string) - Item URL

## Sales locator item (object)
+ Company (string) - Company ItemName
+ IdNo (string) - ID NO
+ Person (string) - Person name
+ Street (string) - Street name
+ PoBox (string) - Po Box
+ Zipcode (string) - Zipcode
+ City (string) - City name
+ Region (string) - Region name
+ Country (string) - Country name
+ Phone (string) - Phone number
+ Mobile (string) - Mobile number
+ Fax (string) - Fax number
+ Email (string) - Email address
+ Web (string) - Website address
+ Image (string) - Image URL (relative)
+ MemberShipStartColumn (string) - ???
+ RoleID (string) - ????
+ Plz (string) - ????

## Contact item (object)
+ ContactType (string) - Contact type
+ ContactName (string) - Contact name
+ ContactPhone (string) - Contact Phone
+ ContactFax (string) - Contact Fax
+ ContactMobile (string) - Contact mobile
+ ContactMailLink (object) - Contact Mail ContactMailLink
    + LinkDescription (string) - Link description
    + Mailto (string) - Mailto email address
    + ContactMailSubject (string) - Contact email subject


## Profesionals locator item (object)
+ Name (string) - Name
+ StreetAddress (string) - Street address
+ Zipcode (string) - Zipcode
+ Municipality (string) - Municipality
+ City (string) - City name
+ Country (string) - Country name
+ Telephone (string) - Telephone number
+ Mobile (string) - Mobile number
+ Fax (string) - Fax number
+ WebAddress (string) - Website address
+ TypeName (string) - Type name
+ TypeIcon (string) - Type icon
+ Specialities (array) - Specialitites
+ AdditionalInformation (string) - AdditionalInformation
+ Latitude (string) - Item latitude
+ Longitude (string) - Item longitude





